{"tid":2332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人開心到訓唔著？","createTime":"2016-11-25T19:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-25T21:44:54.000Z","uid":9598,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"218e2b92096553f802cbd529f6433f13923e9642","tid":2332,"uid":9598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:19:33.000Z","msg":"平時返工關係唔會用電腦上高登<br />\nPlus仔未出前用官方app真係用到火都黎<br />\nM版唔洗講，一樣慢一樣廢，到宜家都毫無改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迫住都係放工用返電腦上高登，對某D人黎講真係好唔方便，直到Plus仔出左之後用落同官方個真係差幾個次元<br />\n完全係我呢D毒撚既恩物，比起之前更加多左上高登<br />\nPlus仔陪在我好多個晚上，宣布要熄機果日我真係喊出黎<br />\n人生就好似冇左寄托咁，我以後可以點算！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係今晚lihkg令我既絕望變成希望<br />\n係呢度我感覺到好有安全感，搵番原本家既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇左高登我唔會死，但冇左各位巴打/絲打一齊吹水食花生<br />\n既日子我諗我真係會死，我今晚真係開心到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">真心好多謝HKG+同LIHKG，希望各位可以齊心係呢到建立屬於自己既真民主論壇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，林祖舜我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b07df7ca60cc26815a93220c9d284a7708f0ff9","tid":2332,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e908bc6a0b75f5dc2cae11e87741fa175f3888a4","tid":2332,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=